 #
+# Security context:
+#   AREA is emitted as a workflow step output that flows into the matrix.
+#   We validate it against a fixed allowlist before writing, and we use the
+#   heredoc form for GITHUB_OUTPUT so an unexpected newline in the input can
+#   never inject additional step outputs (GHSA-style output injection).
+#
 # Required env vars:
 #   GITHUB_OUTPUT
 #   EVENT_NAME - "workflow_dispatch" or "schedule"
@@ -12,16 +18,53 @@ set -euo pipefail
 
